What do you plan to build? (you can chan: College students and young builders juggle classes, clubs, internships, applications, deadlines, workouts, side-projects, and life — all spread across Canvas, email, Discord, calendars, Notion, and random tabs. Staying organized becomes a full-time job, and the cost of slipping is real: missed opportunities, all-nighters, skipped classes, and burnout. Existing tools give you lists and calendars; they don’t think for you. Our app is an AI life operating system that automatically pulls tasks and deadlines from everywhere, prioritizes them, and dynamically schedules your day — adjusting in real time when plans change. Instead of asking “what do I need to do?” or manually shuffling tasks, you just wake up and your day is intelligently planned. It’s like having a personal COO for school and life — so you can stop project-managing yourself and actually live and execute.
